==> box - operating system image
command:=> vagrant box add USER/BOX


** creating a varant project

1. Vagrant project = Folder with a VagrantFile
	
	1. mkdir vm1
	2. cd vm1

  ** then initialize the Vagrant project

   3. vagrant init "image name"
   4. vagrant up/ vagrant up [VM_NAME]

  ** login to a particular virtual machine// connect to the virtual machine
  	 vagrant ssh [VM_NAME]

  ** to stop the Virtual machine
  	 vagrant halt [VM]
  	 vagrant reload [VM]

  ** other important commands

  	 vagrant suspend [VM]
  	 vagrant resume [VM]
  	 vagrant destroy [VM]
  	 vagrant

  ** to see all the virtual machine running
  	 vagrant status
  	 







